{"tid":960644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本遊遇「暗黑AV女優」幫點餐　陸網友瘋喊：我可以！","createTime":"2018-12-29T14:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T15:25:50.000Z","uid":212399,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0d4aca179599478595ad0c49e8166f3b13cca306","tid":960644,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:40:13.000Z","msg":"大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n大陸素來有仇日情結，不過近日一則影片在微博上流傳，由於影片裡頭的日本女服務生長得太正，外表還激似知名AV女優吉澤明步，讓大陸網友通通秒融化，大喊「這個，我可以！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3798/d3798258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3798%2Fd3798258.jpg&h=183b6d76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲這位日本女服務生太正，讓網友都融化了。（圖／翻攝自微博，下同）<br />\n這則由微博網友分享的影片近日在網路上瘋傳，網友表示，有群大陸妹子到日本旅遊用餐時，意外捕獲一名超正日本女服務生。畫面中可見2位女生在餐廳裡不斷用中文討論著事情，而一旁等著點餐的日本女服務生可能聽不太懂中文，只能用著呆萌的疑惑表情傻站一邊，可愛的臉蛋不停出現傻氣的表情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3798/d3798257.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3798%2Fd3798257.jpg&h=c11b7fda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼無辜又呆萌的眼神。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3798/d3798256.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3798%2Fd3798256.jpg&h=0db17f44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這可愛又呆萌的一幕全被拍了下來，瞬間成了眾網友的目光焦點，網友直呼「也太好可愛了」、「這個服務員漂亮」、「超級正的啦！」還有眼尖的網友這位正妹女服務生長相激似日本AV女優吉澤明步，直說兩人的外型相似度極高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3798/d3798281.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3798%2Fd3798281.jpg&h=f63b910a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼有網友認為，這名日本女服務生神似AV女優吉澤明步。（圖／翻攝自吉澤明步微博）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3798/d3798280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3798%2Fd3798280.jpg&h=3a919194&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181229/1343588.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181229%2F1343588.htm&d=Uy2xpkpjBMQV3%2BMr4GcBXZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=715cee19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181229/1343588.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e7be350910196174ae7c5e7ee9aafff00010024a","tid":960644,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01b10a5492b269dada7f58c5a031a79eceff592","tid":960644,"uid":226231,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:43:09.000Z","msg":"其實唔撚似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e5f7da13d4d4a4caee266c52f34f7129eb4534","tid":960644,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:44:12.000Z","msg":"會唔會係新題材"},{"pid":"0d612dee95a151a1dd06d0ecd9cc66034c370fa5","tid":960644,"uid":63491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:45:14.000Z","msg":"都唔似"},{"pid":"3b7824d5253881b4ab2f21f6b135a682a1921e41","tid":960644,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:46:04.000Z","msg":"地址呢"},{"pid":"1d4246a3cd61e85afbbcb6211bf627f19155beaf","tid":960644,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:48:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ddb4542a12fc5f0e67200d0cbb5e953bf7db2a0","tid":960644,"uid":151512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e3fd9694ee8a2017c26a853335def7cd6ff516","tid":960644,"uid":155682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:51:12.000Z","msg":"朦朦地我覺得似大面bella多啲"},{"pid":"b264d53aaaae14de4d5c49d839c11afae92639cf","tid":960644,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,